<FIRST>r i AM-BRF--Nepal-Landslide     09-14 0057</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-BRF--Nepal-Landslide,0057</SECOND>
<HEAD>Landslide Kills 16 in Nepal</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KATMANDU, Nepal (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A landslide has killed 16 people in
southwestern Nepal, the Nepalese national news agency RSS reported
Thursday.
   RSS said the landslide occurred Friday in Bajhang district, 288
miles southwest of Katmandu, swept away four houses and 25 head of
cattle and blocked a small river.
